#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:2
msgid "Observability"
msgstr "可观察性"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:4
msgid ""
"LMCache multiprocess mode provides three complementary observability "
"modes: **metrics** (Prometheus counters via OTel), **logging** (Python "
"logging with optional OTel log forwarding), and **tracing** (OTel spans "
"for per-request latency)."
msgstr "LMCache MP 模式（多进程）提供三种互补的可观察性模式：\\ **指标**\\ （通过 OTel 的 Prometheus 计数器）、\\ **日志**\\ （带有可选 OTel 日志转发的 Python 日志记录）和 **追踪**\\ （OTel span，用于每个请求的延迟分析）。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:9
msgid ""
"All three modes are powered by an internal **EventBus** that decouples "
"producers (L1Manager, StorageManager, MPCacheServer) from subscribers."
msgstr "这三种模式都由一个内部的 **EventBus** 提供支持，该总线将生产者（L1Manager、StorageManager、MPCacheServer）与订阅者解耦。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:17
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "快速开始"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:19
msgid ""
"By default, **metrics** and **logging** are enabled; **tracing** is "
"disabled. No extra flags are needed:"
msgstr "默认情况下，\\ **指标**\\ 和\\ **日志记录**\\ 是启用的；\\ **追踪**\\ 是禁用的。无需额外的标志："

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:27
msgid "To enable tracing, supply an OTLP endpoint:"
msgstr "要启用追踪，请提供 OTLP 端点："

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:36
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "配置"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:42
msgid "Argument"
msgstr "参数"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:43
#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:91
msgid "Default"
msgstr "默认"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:44
#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:92
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:45
msgid "``--disable-observability``"
msgstr "``--disable-observability``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:46
#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:50
#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:53
#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:56
msgid "off"
msgstr "关闭"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:47
msgid ""
"Master switch: disable the EventBus entirely (no metrics, logging, or "
"tracing subscribers are registered)."
msgstr "主开关：完全禁用 EventBus（不注册任何指标、日志记录或追踪订阅者）。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:49
msgid "``--disable-metrics``"
msgstr "``--disable-metrics``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:51
msgid "Skip metrics subscribers (Prometheus endpoint is not started)."
msgstr "跳过指标订阅者（Prometheus 端点未启动）。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:52
msgid "``--disable-logging``"
msgstr "``--disable-logging``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:54
msgid "Skip logging subscribers."
msgstr "跳过日志订阅者。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:55
msgid "``--enable-tracing``"
msgstr "``--enable-tracing``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:57
msgid "Register tracing subscribers. Requires ``--otlp-endpoint``."
msgstr "注册追踪订阅者。需要 ``--otlp-endpoint``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:58
msgid "``--event-bus-queue-size``"
msgstr "``--event-bus-queue-size``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:59
msgid "``10000``"
msgstr "``10000``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:60
msgid "Maximum events in the EventBus queue before tail-drop."
msgstr "事件总线队列中最大事件数，超过后将进行尾部丢弃。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:61
msgid "``--otlp-endpoint``"
msgstr "``--otlp-endpoint``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:62
#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:73
#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:79
msgid "*(none)*"
msgstr "(无)"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:63
msgid ""
"OTLP gRPC endpoint (e.g. ``http://localhost:4317``). Used for exporting "
"metrics (push mode) and traces."
msgstr "OTLP gRPC 端点（例如 ``http://localhost:4317``\\ ）。用于导出指标（推送模式）和追踪数据。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:65
msgid "``--prometheus-port``"
msgstr "``--prometheus-port``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:66
msgid "``9090``"
msgstr "``9090``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:67
msgid "Port for the Prometheus ``/metrics`` HTTP endpoint."
msgstr "Prometheus ``/metrics`` HTTP 端点的端口。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:68
msgid "``--metrics-sample-rate``"
msgstr "``--metrics-sample-rate``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:69
msgid "``0.01``"
msgstr "``0.01``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:70
msgid ""
"Fraction of chunks/blocks to track for lifecycle histograms (0, 1.0]. "
"Counters always count all events. Default is 1%."
msgstr "用于生命周期直方图的 chunk/block 采样比例 (0, 1.0]。计数器始终统计所有事件。默认值为 1%。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:72
msgid "``--trace-level``"
msgstr "``--trace-level``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:74
msgid ""
"Enable trace recording at the given level. Currently only ``storage`` is "
"supported (records ``StorageManager`` public-API calls for offline "
"replay). When unset, trace recording is off. See :ref:`trace-recording` "
"for details."
msgstr "在指定级别启用追踪录制。目前仅支持 ``storage``\\ （记录 ``StorageManager`` 公共 API 调用以便离线回放）。未设置时，追踪录制关闭。详情请参见 :ref:`trace-recording`。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:78
msgid "``--trace-output``"
msgstr "``--trace-output``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:80
msgid ""
"Path to write the trace file. If omitted while ``--trace-level`` is set, "
"a timestamped file under ``$TMPDIR`` is minted (``lmcache-"
"trace-<pid>-<UTC>.lct``) and its path is logged at INFO."
msgstr "追踪文件的写入路径。若设置了 ``--trace-level`` 但省略此项，将在 ``$TMPDIR`` 下自动生成一个带时间戳的文件（\\ ``lmcache-trace-<pid>-<UTC>.lct``\\ ），并以 INFO 级别记录其路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:84
msgid "**Environment variables:**"
msgstr "**环境变量：**"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:90
msgid "Variable"
msgstr "变量"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:93
msgid "``LMCACHE_LOG_LEVEL``"
msgstr "``LMCACHE_LOG_LEVEL``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:94
msgid "``INFO``"
msgstr "``INFO``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/index.rst:95
msgid ""
"Controls the log level for all LMCache loggers. Valid values: ``DEBUG``, "
"``INFO``, ``WARNING``, ``ERROR``, ``CRITICAL``."
msgstr "控制所有 LMCache 日志记录器的日志级别。有效值：\\ ``DEBUG``\\ 、\\ ``INFO``\\ 、\\ ``WARNING``\\ 、\\ ``ERROR``\\ 、\\ ``CRITICAL``\\ 。"

